  "date": "2025-08-05 13:00:00",
  "author": "Walter Korman, Harpreet Arora",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_content__K4T54\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:24px\" data-customer-story=\"false\">\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack w-full flex-wrap gap-4\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:space-between;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:6px\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\">1<!-- --> min read</p>\n    </div><time class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK order-2 md:order-3\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\" datetime=\"2025-08-05\">Aug 5, 2025</time>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">You can now access gpt-oss-20b and gpt-oss-120b by <a href=\"https://openai.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">OpenAI</a>, open-weight reasoning models designed to push the open model frontier, using Vercel's <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI Gateway</a> with no other provider accounts required.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">AI Gateway lets you call the model with a consistent unified API and just a single string update, track usage and cost, and configure performance optimizations, retries, and failover for higher than provider-average uptime.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">To use it with the <a href=\"https://v5.ai-sdk.dev/docs/introduction\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI SDK v5</a>, start by installing the package:</p>\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-code-block_wrapper__o0MQx\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block_wrapper__t6FCO blog-code-block_codeBlock__Nxxa0\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block_copyButton__uo5Yu code-block_copyFloatingButton__PsMvB\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-bash code-block_pre___OLfy blog-code-block_maxHeight__Qz59l\"><code class=\"code-block_code__isn_V\"><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token function\">pnpm</span><span class=\"token plain\"> i ai</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Then set the model to either <code>openai/gpt-oss-20b</code> or <code>openai/gpt-oss-120b</code>:</p>\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-code-block_wrapper__o0MQx\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block_wrapper__t6FCO blog-code-block_codeBlock__Nxxa0\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block_copyButton__uo5Yu code-block_copyFloatingButton__PsMvB\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-tsx code-block_pre___OLfy blog-code-block_maxHeight__Qz59l\"><code class=\"code-block_code__isn_V\"><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> streamText </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'ai'</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> result </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">streamText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"true\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"openai/gpt-oss-120b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token comment\">// or openai/gpt-oss-20b</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  prompt</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"Generate an ansi animation of sutro tower\"</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Includes built-in <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/observability\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">observability</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway#configuring-your-own-provider-keys-byok\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Bring Your Own Key support</a>, and intelligent <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/provider-options\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">provider routing</a> with automatic retries.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">To deliver high performance and reliability to gpt-oss, AI Gateway leverages multiple model providers under the hood, including Groq, Baseten, Cerebras, and Huggingface.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Learn more about <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI Gateway</a> and view the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">new AI Gateway model leaderboard</a>.</p>\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack note_note__PYdoH\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:12px\">\n    <svg class=\"note_icon__166Sz\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:var(--ds-gray-900)\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n     <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8 14.5C11.5899 14.5 14.5 11.5899 14.5 8C14.5 4.41015 11.5899 1.5 8 1.5C4.41015 1.5 1.5 4.41015 1.5 8C1.5 11.5899 4.41015 14.5 8 14.5ZM8 16C12.4183 16 16 12.4183 16 8C16 3.58172 12.4183 0 8 0C3.58172 0 0 3.58172 0 8C0 12.4183 3.58172 16 8 16ZM6.25 7H7H7.74999C8.30227 7 8.74999 7.44772 8.74999 8V11.5V12.25H7.24999V11.5V8.5H7H6.25V7ZM8 6C8.55229 6 9 5.55228 9 5C9 4.44772 8.55229 4 8 4C7.44772 4 7 4.44772 7 5C7 5.55228 7.44772 6 8 6Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" />\n    </svg>\n    <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400\">Vercel is a launch partner for the release of gpt-oss, and thank OpenAI for their collaboration in ensuring day 1 readiness for AI Gateway and its customers.</p>\n   </div><a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_wrapper__HAZou\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_content__cprIT\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--sm-stack-direction:column;--md-stack-direction:row;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--sm-stack-gap:16px;--md-stack-gap:24px;--lg-stack-gap:24px;--xl-stack-gap:24px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:4px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK inline-cta_text___NNFK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:1rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400\"><span class=\"inline-cta_icon__leU_J\">\n        <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n         <g clip-path=\"url(#clip0_872_3186)\">\n          <circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"8\" r=\"7.25\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" />\n          <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8 4.5L11.5 10.625H4.5L8 4.5Z\" fill=\"var(--ds-gray-100)\" />\n         </g> <defs>\n          <clipPath id=\"clip0_872_3186\">\n           <rect width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"white\" />\n          </clipPath>\n         </defs>\n        </svg></span><strong>AI Gateway: Track top AI models by usage</strong></p>\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:1rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\">The AI Gateway model leaderboard ranks the most used models over time by total token volume across all traffic through the Gateway. Updates regularly.</p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:flex-start;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK inline-cta_cta__pdLRm\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:500\">View the leaderboard</p>\n     </div>\n    </div></a>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__AkDZP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel AI 网关现在支持 OpenAI 的 gpt-oss-20b 和 gpt-oss-120b 开放权重模型，提供统一 API、监控能力和性能优化。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel AI 网关现在支持 OpenAI 的 gpt-oss-20b 和 gpt-oss-120b 开放权重模型，提供统一 API、监控能力和性能优化。",
  "summary": "本文宣布，Vercel AI 网关现已支持 OpenAI 的 gpt-oss-20b 和 gpt-oss-120b 开放权重推理模型，开发者无需额外的提供商账户即可使用。它强调了 AI 网关的核心功能，包括统一 API、使用情况和成本跟踪，以及用于性能、重试和故障转移的配置，以确保高正常运行时间。该集成利用了多个底层模型提供商，如 Groq、Baseten、Cerebras 和 Huggingface，以增强可靠性。本文提供了一个使用 AI SDK v5 的快速代码示例，以演示如何集成这些新模型。Vercel 强调其作为 gpt-oss 启动合作伙伴的角色及其与 OpenAI 的合作。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vercel AI 网关现在支持 OpenAI 的 gpt-oss 模型。",
      "explanation": "此集成允许开发人员通过统一的 API 轻松访问这些开放权重模型，从而简化了 Vercel 生态系统中的开发和部署。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 网关为 AI 模型管理提供了强大的功能。",
      "explanation": "统一 API、使用情况跟踪、性能优化和自动重试等功能增强了 AI 应用程序的可靠性和运营效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该集成使用多个提供商来实现高性能和可靠性。",
      "explanation": "通过利用 Groq 和 Huggingface 等提供商，AI 网关确保了 gpt-oss 模型的最佳性能和弹性，从而使用户受益于更好的正常运行时间。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "您现在可以通过 Vercel AI 网关访问 OpenAI 的 gpt-oss-20b 和 gpt-oss-120b 开放权重推理模型，无需其他提供商帐户，助力开放模型发展。",
    "AI 网关允许您使用统一 API 和一个字符串更新来调用模型，跟踪使用情况和成本，并配置性能优化、重试和故障转移，以实现高于提供商平均水平的正常运行时间。",
    "为了向 gpt-oss 提供高性能和可靠性，AI 网关在底层利用了多个模型提供商，包括 Groq、Baseten、Cerebras 和 Huggingface。"
  ],
